- this program is in released state: only issues will be solved
* 20200203 beta 3 - second
- Utility assmime.py: it uses /etc/mime.types no more; 
  it now uses regular files: this means that the program can only 
  manage the known extensions. 
* 20200203 beta 3
- delete button: no more trashcan for items not in HOME dir or in mass storages
- "Open with..." function: improved compatibility with local desktop files (Exec field: "$HOME" and "~" will be replaced with path)
- improvements
- utility assmime: improvements (while some issues seem to be unrelated to this program)
* 20200201 beta 2
- added a basic utility for managing mimetype associations (folder Utility)
- The trash can button opens one tab at a time
- improvements
